                The Motorcycle & Small Engine Technician – Pre-Apprenticeship program at North American Trade Schools at the London campus provides technical training for individuals looking for a rewarding career in the motorcycle, small engine and outdoor equipment repair field.
                <br /><br />
                There are employment opportunities for graduates of the Motorcycle and Small Engine Repair Technician - Pre-Apprenticeship graduates in London, Thamesford, Lucan, Strathroy, St. Thomas, Ingersoll, Stratford, Kitchener-Waterloo, Brampton, Toronto, Mississauga, Scarborough, Milton, Burlington, Oakville, Hamilton and other cities across southern Ontario.
